module.exports = {"title":"Regex to Remove non ASCII Characters","date":"2010-01-06T00:00:00.000Z","tags":"ascii,regex","__content":"<p>I had a file that I wanted to remove non-ascii characters from. I did some searching, got some hints, and came up with this:</p>\n<pre class=\"sh_sh\">\ncat filename.txt | sed -r \"s/[^\\x20-\\x7E|\\n|\\ |\\t]//g\" > newfilename.txt\n</pre>\n\n<p>Worked for me on version Squeeze of Debian GNU/Linux.</p>\n"}

