module.exports = {"title":"NewBay Media LLC Music Player Network","date":"2010-01-11T00:00:00.000Z","tags":"spam","__content":"<p>I&#39;ve been getting spam-like emails about music lately. The emails claim:</p>\n<blockquote class=\"svxlb\"><pre>\nYou have received this message because you previously gave your email address to NewBay Media LLC.\n</pre></blockquote>\n\n<p>I have to disagree!</p>\n<p>I unsubscribed. If they email again, I will conclude that these guys are indeed spammers.</p>\n"}

