module.exports = {"title":"Looking Forward to 1.9.2","date":"2010-03-22T00:00:00.000Z","tags":"1.9,ruby","__content":"<p>I was doing some research on Ruby garbage collection (GC) and found this post about Ruby 1.9.2:</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://fukamachi.org/wp/2009/12/04/incredibly-impressed-with-ruby-1-9-2/\">Incredibly impressed with 1.9.2</a></p>\n<blockquote>\nPerformance is up around 20% on 1.9.1, too.\n</blockquote>\n\n<p>I&#39;m fairly locked into place with 1.9.1 for now, but it will be awesome to install 1.9.2 when I&#39;m ready!</p>\n"}

