module.exports = {"title":"Nexista and PBooks Now Github","date":"2010-07-09T00:00:00.000Z","tags":"git,php","__content":"<p>Just spreading the good news - the two PHP projects I work on the most, <a href=\"http://www.nexista.org/\">Nexista</a> (a web application development framework) and <a href=\"http://www.pbooks.org/\">PBooks</a> (an open source accounting web app) are now hosted at Github.</p>\n<p>In the process, I went through PBooks and made sure the code is totally up-to-date. I&#39;ve still got some organizing to do, but its a big step forward.</p>\n<p>In the several months I&#39;ve been using <a href=\"http://www.docunext.com/\">Git</a>, I&#39;m really amazed by how useful it is!</p>\n"}

