module.exports = {"title":"Blackberry Not Receiving Emails RESOLVED","date":"2010-08-16T00:00:00.000Z","tags":"troubleshooting","__content":"<p>A client just called up with a question about their email service, specifically <strong>their Blackberry device was not receiving emails</strong> and they were wondering if I could help.</p>\n<p>While I&#39;ve setup Blackberries to receive email before, I&#39;m not too familiar with troubleshooting them. So what to do when your Blackberry isn&#39;t receiving emails? I did some internet spelunking and found some advice: fully reboot your phone!</p>\n<p>So I advised my client - if you want to get your Blackberry to start receiving email once again, try fully rebooting it, and by fully rebooting it, I mean:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Turn off the Blackberry</li>\n<li>Remove the battery from the Blackberry</li>\n<li>Leave the battery out for at least thirty seconds</li>\n<li>Put the battery back in the Blackberry and turn it on</li>\n</ol>\n<p>While mileage may vary, this solution restored the email service to my client&#39;s Blackberry. :-)</p>\n"}

