module.exports = {"title":"Active Polling for Select Outlook 2007 with GMail IMAP Accounts","date":"2010-10-05T00:00:00.000Z","tags":"imap,outlook","__content":"<p>I&#39;m helping a client setup selective active polling (send/receive) for only one GMail IMAP account, and very infrequent polling for an archival GMail IMAP account.</p>\n<p>Here are the links I&#39;ve found so far:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.webster.edu/helpdesk/inbox_optimize/send-recieve-outlook.html\">http://www.webster.edu/helpdesk/inbox_optimize/send-recieve-outlook.html</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://email.about.com/od/outlooktips/qt/et_send_receive.htm\">http://email.about.com/od/outlooktips/qt/et_send_receive.htm</a></li>\n</ul>\n"}

