module.exports = {"title":"libx264","date":"2010-10-28T00:00:00.000Z","tags":"audio","__content":"<p>I&#39;m using new video conversion options:</p>\n<pre class=\"sh_sh\">\nffmpeg -r 1 -i ~/Music/tmp.avi -f avi -acodec mp2 -ab 64k -ar 22050 -ac 1 -vcodec libx264 -vpre veryfast -b 768k -bt 768k -threads 2 ~/Music/tmp2.avi\n</pre>\n\n<p>Additional bonus, rotate a video 90 degrees with mencoder:</p>\n<pre class=\"sh_sh\">\nmencoder -vf rotate=1 -o 2010-10-14_09-10-04_980_.3gp  -oac pcm -ovc raw 2010-10-14_09-10-04_980.3gp\n</pre>\n\n<p>The &quot;veryfast&quot; preset doesn&#39;t come on Ubuntu by default:</p>\n<pre>\ncoder=1\nflags=+loop\ncmp=+chroma\npartitions=+parti8x8+parti4x4+partp8x8+partb8x8\nme_method=hex\nsubq=4\nme_range=16\ng=250\nkeyint_min=25\nsc_threshold=40\ni_qfactor=0.71\nb_strategy=1\nqcomp=0.6\nqmin=10\nqmax=51\nqdiff=4\nbf=3\nrefs=2\ndirectpred=1\ntrellis=1\nflags2=+bpyramid-mixed_refs+wpred+dct8x8+fastpskip\nwpredp=1\nrc_lookahead=20\n</pre>\n\n"}

