module.exports = {"title":"Working on Making My Laptop Cooler Still","date":"2011-03-26T00:00:00.000Z","tags":"laptop,power","__content":"<p>This is a never ending challenge for me. Here&#39;s my latest effort:</p>\n<pre class=\"sh_sh\">\necho 0 > /sys/devices/system/cpu/cpu1/online\necho 15 > /proc/sys/vm/dirty_background_ratio\necho 55 > /proc/sys/vm/dirty_ratio\necho 6000 > /proc/sys/vm/dirty_writeback_centisecs\necho 9000 > /proc/sys/vm/dirty_expire_centisecs\nhdparm -B 1 -S12 /dev/sda\necho 1 > /sys/module/snd_hda_intel/parameters/power_save\nxbacklight -set 90\nhal-disable-polling --device /dev/scd0\n# to enable this again:\n# hal-disable-polling --device /dev/scd0 --enable-polling\nexit 0\n</pre>\n\n"}

