module.exports = {"title":"Another Awesome Experience with Debian Squeeze Xen 4.0 and OpenVZ and some Squeeze driver issues","date":"2011-04-10T00:00:00.000Z","__content":"<p>I am so utterly impressed with Debian. They are pushing the envelope - seriously!</p>\n<p>The remarkable factor with Debian, Xen, and OpenVZ is simply that: the stable version of Debian supports a Xen 4.0 (a <strong>very modern</strong> impelementation) kernel, and with the help of pygrub, all different kernels can be used within the virtual machines.</p>\n"}

